1
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,540
Of course I'm not here

2
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:02,019
as the auditee's rep.

3
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,379
But if

4
00:02:03,379 --> 00:02:05,079
you're here as my boyfriend,

5
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,400
you're way over the line.

6
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,139
This is my job.

7
00:02:08,819 --> 00:02:10,000
I can handle it.

8
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:18,819
Hello?

9
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,180
Safe.

10
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,580
Okay.

11
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,099
Just wait for me at the gas station.

12
00:02:26,539 --> 00:02:27,180
Miao Jing...

13
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:27,680
And

14
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,759
if you ever

15
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,080
pull another stunt

16
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,719
without telling me again,

17
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,740
I'm really not coming home.

18
00:02:46,419 --> 00:02:47,300
Are you coming home?

19
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,319
You told me

20
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,300
to go to a colleague's.

21
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,500
Forget I said that.

22
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,560
I got something to do.

23
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,639
What?

24
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:54,680
Picking up a colleague.

25
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:55,500
Cen Ye?

26
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,699
Get out.

27
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,480
Three hundred.

28
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,519
Been waiting long?

29
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,600
Grab two bottles of water.

30
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,480
Sir, how much?

31
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,139
Three hundred.

32
00:04:48,939 --> 00:04:49,399
Sir.

33
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,740
Sir!

34
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,860
Your tank's almost full.

35
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,720
Did you just fill up?

36
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:55,220
Never mind. Just top it off.

37
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,500
Okay.

38
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,560
Hi.

39
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,399
Ring up number 3 and 4 together.

40
00:05:05,699 --> 00:05:06,720
Number 3's done. Three hundred.

41
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,399
Number 4 will be a moment.

42
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,519
Mr. Chen?

43
00:05:14,019 --> 00:05:15,300
You've got business out here too?

44
00:05:17,699 --> 00:05:18,779
I'll give you a ride back later.

45
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:19,560
I'll

46
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,860
hitch a ride with Ms. Miao.

47
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,000
She's taking me back.

48
00:05:23,019 --> 00:05:23,639
What,

49
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,199
you bought a car before you even

50
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:26,160
have a license?

51
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,160
Yeah, it's been a while. A bit rusty.

52
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,800
Mr. Chen, you're getting heated?

53
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,439
You head back first.

54
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,560
Shall we go?

55
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:42,019
Thanks for the gas.

56
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:43,000
I'll treat you to a meal.

57
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,899
I'll keep Mr. Cen for a quick work chat.

58
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:09,060
Ms. Miao, you've learned to bite back?

59
00:06:09,819 --> 00:06:10,379
What?

60
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:12,079
Nothing.

61
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,279
Just never knew

62
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,259
you had this side to you.

63
00:06:14,579 --> 00:06:15,540
Makes me a little jealous.

64
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:18,379
What are you laughing at?

65
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:21,399
You're reminiscing with me.

66
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,000
It's hard for me to know

67
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,759
how to respond properly.

68
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,680
I'm your subordinate after all.

69
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,480
I need to think

70
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,759
before I speak to my boss.

71
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:31,060
It's after work now.

72
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,180
Not your boss reminiscing with you.

73
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,680
Do you guys

74
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,519
all think office romance

75
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:39,620
is exciting

76
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,839
and attractive to girls?

77
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,759
You're pretty worked up.

78
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:45,339
Investigation didn't go well today?

79
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,680
Haoyun's fleet

80
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,740
swapped plates

81
00:06:47,740 --> 00:06:48,600
before crossing the border.

82
00:06:48,779 --> 00:06:49,579
Tao Jiang was there too.

83
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:51,879
Tao Jiang was there?

84
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:52,800
Yeah.

85
00:06:53,379 --> 00:06:54,199
But I was too far.

86
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,439
I didn't get a clear shot.

87
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:56,600
That fleet wasn't

88
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,920
the one Haoyun registered.

89
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,199
If I hand this

90
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,500
over to Hongshen,

91
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:01,519
We're still missing

92
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,939
some data to back it up.

93
00:07:03,139 --> 00:07:04,060
They're careful.

94
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:06,079
Guess we'll have to smoke them out.

95
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,500
But

96
00:07:08,339 --> 00:07:09,519
we've got the bait ready.

97
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,560
You mean Ding Lei?

98
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,379
But means putting you in a tough spot.

99
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,540
When Chen Yi finds out,

100
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,600
it won't be just a few threats

101
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,540
that settle it.

102
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,680
You're not asking what he said to me?

103
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,839
I can guess.

104
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:44,060
Mr. Cen,

105
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,480
I'm a simple man. I don't get

106
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,240
your way of working.

107
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,779
Professionally, I've got nothing to say.

108
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,519
But personally,

109
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,279
if you ever put Miao Jing

110
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,120
in harm's way again

111
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,819
for your career or some plan,

112
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:58,720
I'll make sure you regret it.

113
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,040
Hello.

114
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,660
Here's your ID.

115
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,100
Please keep it safe.

116
00:08:07,379 --> 00:08:07,860
Okay.

117
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:08,600
Thanks.

118
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,480
Let me see your ID.

119
00:08:11,259 --> 00:08:11,759
Hi.

120
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:12,560
I need to file a report.

121
00:08:13,019 --> 00:08:13,360
Hello.

122
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,420
Truck scrape?

123
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,339
Was the other driver

124
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:27,459
not in the vehicle when it happened?

125
00:08:28,699 --> 00:08:30,079
It was out in the middle of nowhere.

126
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,120
I didn't dare wait around.

127
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,200
So I took a photo

128
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,000
of the plate.

129
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,340
This one.

130
00:08:36,539 --> 00:08:37,379
Could you see if you can

131
00:08:37,379 --> 00:08:38,279
contact the owner?

132
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,460
I'd like to file an insurance claim.

133
00:08:39,580 --> 00:08:40,259
Sure. One moment.

134
00:09:06,139 --> 00:09:06,879
Please write this down.

135
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:09,480
The owner's contact info is...

136
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:18,279
Hello?

137
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:19,779
What is it?

138
00:09:23,259 --> 00:09:23,960
You both

139
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,299
did two runs yesterday, right?

140
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:25,860
Yes.

141
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,360
- Mr. Tao.
- Mr. Tao.

142
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,399
Have a seat.

143
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,220
Mr. Tao, here's the schedule.

144
00:09:48,539 --> 00:09:49,200
Where's Bai?

145
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,320
I said no one's late

146
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:50,919
for the meeting.

147
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:52,580
Bai's truck

148
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:53,259
got scraped.

149
00:09:53,299 --> 00:09:54,639
He went to the traffic police station.

150
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,480
Scraped?

151
00:09:55,779 --> 00:09:56,080
Yeah.

152
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,340
How's there a scrape now of all times?

153
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,039
Which plate?

154
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,700
His own truck.

155
00:10:03,259 --> 00:10:04,279
Call Bai.

156
00:10:04,299 --> 00:10:05,059
Keep calling till he picks up.

157
00:10:05,139 --> 00:10:05,940
Meeting's cancelled today!

158
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,139
Why's it cancelled all of a sudden?

159
00:10:08,139 --> 00:10:08,899
Meeting's off?

160
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,139
Who told you to come?

161
00:10:27,139 --> 00:10:27,820
I came on my own.

162
00:10:28,179 --> 00:10:28,899
Bai doesn't know you.

163
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:30,120
I'll tell him

164
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,039
everything's taken care of.

165
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:31,700
You leave now.

166
00:10:32,419 --> 00:10:33,519
Whose number did you leave as the reporter?

167
00:10:34,139 --> 00:10:34,840
Chen Yi, do you even know

168
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,720
what you're doing?

169
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,080
If you want to

170
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,740
keep working your case,

171
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:42,460
then leave.

172
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,440
Mr. Chen.

173
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:51,720
Mr. Chen?

174
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:54,919
Mr. Chen?

175
00:10:57,899 --> 00:10:58,399
Sorry.

176
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,460
Mr. Chen!

177
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:01,820
Bai.

178
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:02,559
Mr. Chen.

179
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,360
Um,

180
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:04,120
Mr. Tao's asking

181
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,159
which mediation room we're in.

182
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,840
That way. Number three.

183
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:08,279
Okay.

184
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:09,019
Let's go.

185
00:11:20,659 --> 00:11:21,080
Hello.

186
00:11:25,019 --> 00:11:25,419
Mr. Tao.

187
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:26,179
Where's the person who filed the report?

188
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,000
Just a regular accident.

189
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,279
They already paid up

190
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:32,179
and left.

191
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,059
What good is money?

192
00:11:34,419 --> 00:11:35,120
Do you know

193
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,879
how many eyes

194
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:36,620
are on us right now?

195
00:11:37,259 --> 00:11:39,019
That plate's only been used a few times.

196
00:11:39,299 --> 00:11:39,960
And it just happens to

197
00:11:40,179 --> 00:11:41,299
get scraped

198
00:11:41,299 --> 00:11:42,240
in the middle of nowhere?

199
00:11:43,139 --> 00:11:43,440
Well...

200
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,059
Trucks

201
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,840
all have blind spots.

202
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,419
It's normal

203
00:11:48,419 --> 00:11:49,379
we didn't notice.

204
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:54,419
Bai,

205
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,500
this isn't about a scrape.

206
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,899
Someone's digging into us.

207
00:11:59,299 --> 00:12:00,039
Where's Chen Yi?

208
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:00,860
Where is he?

209
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:03,779
Mr-Mr. Chen was just...

210
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,480
Someone was indeed behind this.

211
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:08,679
The audit team

212
00:12:09,019 --> 00:12:09,940
is onto us now.

213
00:12:10,299 --> 00:12:10,940
What do you mean?

214
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:12,860
The one who filed the report

215
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,720
is Ding Lei, the head of Mingtong's

216
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:15,740
audit team.

217
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:23,200
His warehouse in the old district

218
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:24,820
was caught by Cen Ye for freight fraud.

219
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,179
To throw Mingtong off his trail,

220
00:12:27,700 --> 00:12:28,659
Ding Lei

221
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:29,360
set his sights

222
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,200
on Bai's truck.

223
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,080
Passing the buck.

224
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,120
Pretty clever.

225
00:12:36,779 --> 00:12:38,080
If he keeps digging,

226
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,960
Cen Ye won't have time for him anymore.

227
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:41,360
We'll be toast

228
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,559
even if we survive.

229
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:47,740
I'll go tell

230
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:48,840
Mr. Zhang about this.

231
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,419
You go remind him

232
00:12:51,179 --> 00:12:52,340
to keep his mouth shut.

233
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:57,419
Come in.

234
00:13:01,899 --> 00:13:02,659
You wanted to see me, Mr. Chen?

235
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:03,679
Sit.

236
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,200
I hear Mr. Cen

237
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,340
has been on a roll

238
00:13:15,340 --> 00:13:15,879
in your team lately?

239
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,539
I've got

240
00:13:19,539 --> 00:13:21,000
resources and connections.

241
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,179
Truth is,

242
00:13:22,179 --> 00:13:23,039
I just lack opportunities.

243
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,399
He won't be above me forever.

244
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:28,840
Really?

245
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:30,740
But I think

246
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,740
he's about to bring you down.

247
00:13:36,299 --> 00:13:37,000
What do you mean?

248
00:13:41,659 --> 00:13:42,740
Just intercepted this package

249
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:43,460
from Cen Ye.

250
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:44,600
See for yourself.

251
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,279
How did he get all this?

252
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,659
You left a mess

253
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:17,700
and Cen Ye found dirt on you.

254
00:14:17,779 --> 00:14:18,720
What's the point of getting mad now?

255
00:14:18,899 --> 00:14:19,440
I'm telling you,

256
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:20,580
if I hadn't stopped it,

257
00:14:20,879 --> 00:14:22,200
this letter would've been mailed out.

258
00:14:22,379 --> 00:14:23,240
Then not just you,

259
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:24,740
but Haoyun would be screwed too.

260
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:25,500
No way.

261
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:26,419
Absolutely not.

262
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,340
Haoyun's waiting for

263
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:28,399
that final payment from Hongshen.

264
00:14:28,679 --> 00:14:29,840
Isn't Cen Ye afraid of

265
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,240
tanking this whole IPO?

266
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,080
What are you thinking?

267
00:14:35,679 --> 00:14:36,840
Still don't get it?

268
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:38,580
Either way,

269
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:39,559
you and Mr. Wang go down.

270
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,000
Hongshen and I foot the bill.

271
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:54,399
Mr. Chen,

272
00:14:55,399 --> 00:14:56,179
since you managed to

273
00:14:56,179 --> 00:14:57,139
intercept this letter,

274
00:14:58,179 --> 00:14:59,000
you've already got a plan,

275
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,500
right?

276
00:15:00,779 --> 00:15:01,320
If this

277
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,080
gets exposed,

278
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,720
nobody wins.

279
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,519
This matter

280
00:15:12,740 --> 00:15:13,919
dies in this room.

281
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,279
Hongshen can't find out.

282
00:15:15,919 --> 00:15:16,940
You resign now.

283
00:15:17,679 --> 00:15:18,659
I'll handle Mr. Wang.

284
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:20,820
Resign?

285
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:27,980
If you don't want your reputation ruined,

286
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:29,820
get the hell out.

287
00:15:40,899 --> 00:15:42,200
Didn't expect you to have such guts.

288
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:44,360
When you asked me for the courier slip,

289
00:15:44,639 --> 00:15:45,879
you didn't say it was for this.

290
00:15:49,019 --> 00:15:49,919
But the problem's solved.

291
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:51,360
Right?

292
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,139
You're hiding things from both sides.

293
00:15:54,559 --> 00:15:55,240
Zhang Bin

294
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,179
won't be that easy to fool.

295
00:16:21,379 --> 00:16:21,860
Mr. Zhang.

296
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:23,360
He's here.

297
00:16:23,879 --> 00:16:24,879
Alright. Send him in.

298
00:16:34,299 --> 00:16:34,820
Mr. Zhang.

299
