900
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:07,659
through the highs and lows of life,

901
00:39:08,420 --> 00:39:10,440
you will always walk hand in hand,

902
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,699
forever and always.

903
00:39:12,820 --> 00:39:14,900
Wonderful!

904
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:16,300
Miao Jing, nice!

905
00:39:19,579 --> 00:39:19,900
Alright.

906
00:39:19,900 --> 00:39:20,840
Thank you.

907
00:39:30,699 --> 00:39:31,940
The pool hall

908
00:39:33,139 --> 00:39:34,699
never felt this empty before.

909
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,380
Bo said

910
00:39:40,639 --> 00:39:41,559
you gave him fifty thousand

911
00:39:41,559 --> 00:39:42,800
when he bought his place.

912
00:39:50,940 --> 00:39:51,539
I'm

913
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:53,500
a single man.

914
00:39:54,059 --> 00:39:56,139
I don't need much money.

915
00:39:57,780 --> 00:39:58,260
Yi,

916
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:00,019
I haven't touched a single dime of

917
00:40:00,019 --> 00:40:01,099
the pool hall dividends you gave me.

918
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:03,960
I just lent it to Bo.

919
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:08,059
You'll be

920
00:40:08,059 --> 00:40:10,219
Bo's kids' number one godfather.

921
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:11,659
And I'll be number two.

922
00:40:13,039 --> 00:40:14,059
I know how you are.

923
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:16,940
You always do things quietly.

924
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,179
But we remember

925
00:40:22,139 --> 00:40:23,139
all the good you do.

926
00:40:24,860 --> 00:40:25,619
Don't keep things

927
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,059
bottled up.

928
00:40:31,719 --> 00:40:32,699
Just tell us anytime.

929
00:40:36,739 --> 00:40:37,539
Alright, Yi.

930
00:40:43,699 --> 00:40:44,659
I just want to imagine

931
00:40:45,260 --> 00:40:46,019
that one day,

932
00:40:47,380 --> 00:40:48,679
Bo and Li Qiao

933
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:50,619
would be with their kids,

934
00:40:51,940 --> 00:40:52,460
you

935
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:54,440
would be with

936
00:40:56,659 --> 00:40:57,619
your future wife

937
00:40:58,219 --> 00:40:59,300
and your kids,

938
00:41:01,019 --> 00:41:01,860
and

939
00:41:03,059 --> 00:41:03,860
all of us

940
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:05,260
would be out

941
00:41:05,699 --> 00:41:07,579
on a big grassy field.

942
00:41:07,619 --> 00:41:08,900
No one else. Just us.

943
00:41:09,420 --> 00:41:10,460
We'd go camping.

944
00:41:12,739 --> 00:41:13,780
No worries.

945
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:15,940
Just relaxing.

946
00:41:24,099 --> 00:41:25,699
It's been hectic lately.

947
00:41:25,860 --> 00:41:27,619
Thanks for all the overtime.

948
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:29,219
Got any plans this weekend?

949
00:41:29,579 --> 00:41:31,079
I'll take everyone to the beach for two days.

950
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:32,619
You pick the spot.

951
00:41:32,719 --> 00:41:33,420
The company

952
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:34,699
covers everything.

953
00:41:34,699 --> 00:41:35,460
For real?

954
00:41:37,619 --> 00:41:38,199
Jing?

955
00:41:41,300 --> 00:41:41,739
No need.

956
00:41:42,079 --> 00:41:43,960
My team's expenses are covered by Mingtong.

957
00:41:46,139 --> 00:41:46,639
Where to?

958
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:49,159
Let's go to Puri Island in Jinguo.

959
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:51,039
It's a rare team outing.

960
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,559
We've got to go abroad.

961
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:53,559
Right, Jing?

962
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:54,280
I'm down.

963
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,199
It's pretty fun there.

964
00:41:56,079 --> 00:41:56,500
What do you think?

965
00:41:57,599 --> 00:41:58,760
What's wrong, Mr. Chen?

966
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:01,940
Let's go to Sannan Island.

967
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,780
Too much hassle with visas

968
00:42:03,780 --> 00:42:05,039
for all of us.

969
00:42:05,619 --> 00:42:06,280
Works for me.

970
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,079
Whatever the boss says.

971
00:42:08,219 --> 00:42:09,000
We're lucky to even go.

972
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:09,880
Alright.

973
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:10,980
Beats being stuck here

974
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:11,980
crunching numbers.

975
00:42:11,980 --> 00:42:13,239
- Absolutely.
- Right.

976
00:42:13,239 --> 00:42:14,440
Alright. No problem.

977
00:42:16,300 --> 00:42:17,420
Should we get some essentials?

978
00:42:17,420 --> 00:42:17,820
Should we?

979
00:42:18,019 --> 00:42:18,300
Yeah.

980
00:42:18,300 --> 00:42:19,039
Can we expense it?

981
00:42:19,239 --> 00:42:20,179
- Go ask about it.
- No way.

982
00:42:20,179 --> 00:42:20,760
Sunscreen.

983
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:21,940
Need to pack sunscreen and stuff.

984
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:22,679
Right.
